d":10595087375,"node_id":"LA_kwDORyqgoc8AAAACd4Q0Dw","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Compendiq/compendiq-ce/labels/security","name":"security","color":"B60205","default":false,"description":"Security-related issues"},{"id":10627238917,"node_id":"LA_kwDORyqgoc8AAAACeW7MBQ","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Compendiq/compendiq-ce/labels/dependencies","name":"dependencies","color":"0366d6","default":false,"description":"Pull requests that update a dependency file"}],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":0,"created_at":"2026-05-14T09:06:31Z","updated_at":"2026-05-14T17:09:41Z","closed_at":"2026-05-14T17:09:41Z","assignee":null,"author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","issue_field_values":[],"type":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"## CVE\n- **ID:** CVE-2026-44458\n- **Package:** `hono@4.12.16` → fix at `hono@4.12.18`\n- **Severity:** MODERATE\n- **Vulnerability class:** CSS Declaration Injection via JSX `style` object values in SSR (CWE-79 / improper encoding)\n- **GHSA:** GHSA-qp7p-654g-cw7p\n- **Transitivity:** transitive — both lockfiles\n\n## Locations\n- `package-lock.json:13393`\n- `mcp-docs/package-lock.json:2225`\n\n## Summary\nThe Hono JSX renderer escapes `style` attribute object values for HTML context but not for CSS context. Characters that act as CSS declaration boundaries — `;`, comment markers, quoted strings, block delimiters — are valid in HTML attribute content and can extend a value beyond its assigned property. An attacker who controls a `style` object value or property name can inject arbitrary CSS declarations, leading to visual manipulation, full-viewport overlays for phishing, outbound requests via `url(...)`, or hijacking of UI affordances. Impact is limited to CSS — no JavaScript execution or HTML attribute breakout.\n\n## Reachability\n**Reachability assessment: not reachable.** Compendiq does not use Hono's JSX renderer anywhere. The backend is Fastify; the frontend is React 19 (rendered client-side via Vite); mcp-docs is Express. No code imports `hono/jsx` or calls `jsx()`/`createElement()`. Hono is transitive via `@modelcontextprotocol/sdk → @hono/node-server`, and the MCP SDK does not invoke the JSX renderer.\n\n## Proposed remediation\nBump root `overrides` to `^4.12.18`:\n\n```json\n\"overrides\": {\n  \"hono\": \"^4.12.18\"\n}\n```\n\nmcp-docs has its own lockfile — add an override there or `npm install` from `mcp-docs/`.\n\n## Related CVEs\n- CVE-2026-44455 (#642 — JSX tag injection, fix at 4.12.16)\n- CVE-2026-44456 (#643 — bodyLimit bypass, fix at 4.12.16)\n- CVE-2026-44457 (#644 — cache leak, fix at 4.12.18)\n- CVE-2026-44459 (JWT NumericDate, fix at 4.12.18)\n\nAll five remediated by `hono@^4.12.18`.\n\n## References\n- GHSA: https://github.com/advisories/GHSA-qp7p-654g-cw7p\n- Advisory: https://github.com/honojs/hono/security/advisories/GHSA-qp7p-654g-cw7p\n\n---\n_Filed by automated Semgrep triage. Source: Semgrep cloud SCA scan._","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Compendiq/compendiq-ce/issues/645/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Compendiq/compendiq-ce/issues/645/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed","pinned_comment":null,"score":1.0},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Compendiq/compendiq-ce/issues/646","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Compendiq/compendiq-ce","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Compendiq/compendiq-ce/issues/646/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Compendiq/compendiq-ce/issues/646/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Compendiq/compendiq-ce/issues/646/events","html_url":"https://github.com/Compendiq/compendiq-ce/issues/646","id":4444650486,"node